      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Ready to find your next dependable ride? This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly and handles confidently on the road, making every trip a pleasure! You'll notice some light cosmetic wear consistent with normal use, but mechanically it's solid and well-maintained. Whether it's your daily commute or a weekend adventure, this vehicle is ready to deliver reliable performance at a great value!",
