    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly Fixer or Basic Transport \u2013 An Honest Poor-Condition Listing! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for the most affordable way to get behind the wheel? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows it. Expect visible wear, cosmetic issues, and mechanical concerns that will likely need attention. It's not a showroom car, but for the right buyer \u2014 whether you're a DIY mechanic, need a short-term solution, or want a project \u2014 it could be exactly what you're after. No surprises here: what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you a full, honest picture so you can shop with confidence. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you'll notice only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use, with no significant rust or major paint damage. The body panels are straight, and the car has a presentable, clean appearance. Inside, the cabin is in solid shape: upholstery shows light use but no tears, stains, or major damage, and all controls and features function as expected. Mechanically, this car is in good working order \u2014 the engine starts reliably, runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts without issue. Brakes, suspension, and steering all feel appropriate for a well-maintained vehicle. You can expect a dependable, comfortable daily driver that has been cared for without being babied. This is a solid, honest choice for a buyer looking for quality without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you an honest, complete picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes typical of a used vehicle, and the body panels are largely free of significant dents or deep scratches. A few small scuffs and light wear marks are visible upon close inspection, consistent with normal everyday use. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with upholstery showing moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light fading on high-contact surfaces, but no tears or major damage. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 all major systems are functioning properly, and there are no known outstanding issues. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for and should serve its next owner well without requiring immediate major investment.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, making it a reliable and sensible choice for buyers seeking dependable used transportation. The exterior shows only minor cosmetic wear consistent with normal use \u2014 think small surface scratches or light scuffs \u2014 but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The paint retains good color and shine, and the body panels are straight without any major dents or damage. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; upholstery shows some wear from regular use but is free of major tears or stains, and all primary controls and features operate as expected. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably \u2014 no major issues to report, though as with any used vehicle, routine maintenance items may come due in the normal course of ownership. This is a solid, honest used car at a fair price \u2014 not a showroom-fresh mint example, but a genuinely dependable vehicle that offers real value for the money.",
      "price": 34000.0,
